snippet.textDisplay: This report was made in the Advent's Zeit, 2 mths ago. What is being done to advise the populace of Early Treatment possibilities in the first 5 days of infection to reduce the necessity of hospitalisation instead of waiting until the disease gets a hold of the immune system. And now we have Omicron. Different ball game.
